The robot always starts at position (0, 0).
The Optical Sensor LED is turned on.
The robot:
Moves along a defined path.
Turns at corners.
Detects obstacles (using Distance or Bumper Sensor).
Detects the colour of an object (using Optical Sensor).
Picks it up (with Arm and pulley).
Delivers it to a shelf location.

